Land and Development Bank of South Africa (LADBSA) bụ ụlọ akụ mmepe nke gọọmentị nwere na Republic of South Africa
E hiwere ụlọ akụ ahụ dị ka ụlọ ọrụ ego mmepe na 1912 site n'aka gọọmentị South Africa
Ebumnobi bụ isi nke LADBSA bụ ịkwalite na ego mmepe na ngalaba ọrụ ugbo nke akụnụba obodo.
Àtụ:Banks of South AfricaÀtụ:Economy of South Africa
